title: UD San Lorenzo de Flumen
text: Unión Deportiva San Lorenzo is a Spanish <a href="List%20of%20football%20clubs%20in%20Spain">football</a> team based in <a href="San%20Lorenzo%20del%20Flumen">San Lorenzo del Flumen</a>, <a href="Lalueza">Lalueza</a>, in the community of <a href="Arag%C3%B3n">Aragón</a>. Founded in 1968, it plays in <a href="Tercera%20Divisi%C3%B3n">Tercera División</a>.
